<div class="bg-white div-with-full-vh" style="height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
  <div class="container d-flex flex-row justify-content-between" style="max-width: 100%; padding: 0 50px;"> <!-- Ensures no overflow and padding is consistent -->
    <!-- Left Column for Text -->
    <div class="col-md-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center"> <!-- Ensures vertical centering within the column -->
      <div>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 50px; font-weight: normal;">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="mb-5">
          <div class="mb-5">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.25em;">Step 1: Sign Up & Create Your Profile</h3>
            <p>Get started in seconds with your email to customize your profile settings.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.25em;">Step 2: Add Your Schedule</h3>
            <p>Connect your calendar or manually input past engagements. This makes your free times visible to group members for easy planning.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.25em;">Step 3: Create Your Group</h3>
            <p>Create a group with a few clicks, and access a collective calendar showcasing everyone's events. This enables you to easily identify a mutual free slot that suits all members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Right Column for Image -->
    <div class="col-md-6 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
      <%= image_tag("Calendar.jpeg", alt: "Features and Benefits", class: "img-fluid", style: "width: 600px; border-radius: 20px;") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

